v 1.0 0.0 0.0
v 0.0 1.0 0.0
vt 0.0 0.0
vt 1.0 0.0
vt 0.0 1.0
usemtl texture
f 1/1 2/2 3/3

o B
v 2.0 0.0 0.0
v 3.0 0.0 0.0
v 2.0 1.0 0.0
vt 0.0 0.0
vt 1.0 0.0
vt 0.0 1.0
usemtl texture
